race.comment: ZARAGOZA (4) ticks plenty of boxes today with the booking of Nash Rawiller. Set to peak after taking good ground off Oui Oui Oui when fifth over 1200m at this track. Can race a little closer with the addition of blinkers. Hard to beat in this suitable race. JAMBALAYA (7) snagged back from the wide gate when a respectable seventh over this trip at Canterbury. Will stalk the tempo and assess on his good win two-back. FIORENZA (13) lightly raced mare who raced without luck when eighth to Oui Oui Oui over 1200m at this track. Drawn out again and goes into the exotics. LET'S GO AGAIN (9) gripped on late at her second run back when a handy sixth over 1200m. Minor place prospects. CLANCY (6) lightly raced gelding resuming. Has the upside to surprise in this tougher contest after showing ability in his first prep. Fitted with the two trials and not to be underestimated.
